---
import researchInterests from '../data/research-interests.json';
---

<div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-8">
  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
    My research interests are in the field of systems optimization, especially in using machine
    learning techniques to optimize operating systems and compilers. These are a few things I have
    been working on:
  </p>
</div>

<ul class="space-y-3">
  {researchInterests.map((interest) => (
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 mt-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary-500 dark:bg-primary-400"></span>
      <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">{interest}</span>
    </li>
  ))}
</ul>
